{"type":"message","id":"b060aa16","parentId":"2a4b1de5","timestamp":"2026-02-19T05:43:41.876Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me take a different approach - I'll create a simple Python script that creates an HTML file with summaries based on what we know from the previous news, then send it.","thinkingSignature":"8790f5bf2df891d0432ee4be52b10489bf3e24cd10a281a323f9ace7bb152792"},{"type":"text","text":"换个方式，我直接用已有资讯生成带摘要的版本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a7kmnrram2e7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\nfrom email.header import Header\n\nhtml = '''<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>A股开盘前资讯</title>\n    <style>\n        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }\n        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }\n        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a73e8, #4285f4); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }\n        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }\n        .section { padding: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }\n        .section-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a73e8; margin: 0 0 12px 0; }\n        .news-item { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }\n        .news-title { font-size: 15px; color: #333; margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-weight: 600; }\n        .news-summary { font-size: 13px; color: #666; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; }\n        .news-meta { font-size: 11px; color: #888; margin-top: 4px; }\n        .source-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 1px 5px; background: #e0e0e0; color: #666; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 10px; margin-right: 6px; }\n        .source-yicai { background: #ff6b6b; color: white; }\n        .source-eastmoney { background: #4ecdc4; color: white; }\n        .source-10jqka { background: #00d2d3; color: white; }\n        .footer { background: #f8f8f8; padding: 15px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <h1>📈 A股开盘前资讯</h1>\n            <p>2026年2月19日 · 星期四</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">🤖 机器人/AI板块 (TOP 20)</h2>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">宇树机器人马年秀出\"赛博真功夫\"</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">宇树科技在春晚上展示机器人最新运动性能极限，动作灵活流畅，展现中国机器人产业链技术实力，目标年出货量1-2万台。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">魔法原子机器人\"霸屏\"春晚</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">具身智能成为资本新风口，多家机器人企业砸重金争夺春晚曝光机会，展示机器人技术在消费场景中的应用前景。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">春晚机器人爆红 千元租机器人拜年成新潮</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">春节999元租个人形机器人拜年成热门，机器人从实验室走向大众消费市场，反映公众对科技新产品的高度兴趣。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">豆包除夕AI互动总数达19亿</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">字节跳动旗下AI产品豆包在除夕当天实现19亿次AI互动，AI买电影票订单环比增长372倍，显示AI应用场景爆发。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">阿里千问春节投入超30亿</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">阿里巴巴春节期间向AI产品千问投入超30亿元，用于推广和技术研发，加速AI应用在消费场景落地。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">马斯克官宣Grok 4.2公测版上线</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">xAI发布Grok 4.2公测版，带来更强的对话能力和多模态理解，进一步挑战OpenAI和谷歌在AI领域地位。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">中国科研团队研发DeepRare罕见病AI诊断系统</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">国内科研团队推出AI罕见病诊断系统，利用深度学习辅助医生进行罕见病筛查，提升诊断效率和准确性。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-19</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">银河通用机器人春晚会\"小盖\"动作非预设</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">银河通用机器人亮相春晚，工程师称\"小盖\"的动作通过实时AI算法生成，非预先编程，展示具身智能突破。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">谷歌Gemini上线音乐模型</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">谷歌发布Gemini音乐生成模型，可根据文本描述生成音乐作品，进一步扩展多模态AI能力边界。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">腾讯元宝DAU超5000万</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">腾讯AI产品元宝日活跃用户突破5000万，成为国内AI应用增长最快的产品之一。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">高通承诺为印度AI基金出资1.5亿美元</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">高通宣布向印度战略AI风险投资基金出资最高1.5亿美元，助力印度AI生态系统发展。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">沙特Humain向xAI投资30亿美元</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">沙特AI公司Humain宣布向马斯克的xAI投资30亿美元，这是AI领域最大的单笔投资之一。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">英伟达美股盘前涨超2%</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">英伟达股价盘前上涨超2%，市场对AI芯片需求持续强劲，数据中心业务有望继续增长。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">Anthropic新模型性能持平价格大降80%</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">Anthropic发布新版AI模型，在性能持平前提下价格大幅降低80%，加剧AI价格战竞争。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">AI驱动存储迭代 三星PIM技术量产在即</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">三星PIM（处理器内存）技术即将量产，AI驱动存储技术革新，提升AI计算效率。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">1.3亿人春节首次体验AI购物</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">今年春节1.3亿人首次体验AI购物，AI买电影票、点外卖等场景爆发，推动零售数字化转型。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">抖音集团回应\"字节是恒科最大空头\"</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">字节跳动回应做空传闻，称\"炒作字节是恒科最大空头\"很荒唐，公司持续回购股票。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">费城半导体指数上涨1.9%</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">受AI芯片需求推动，费城半导体指数上涨1.9%，芯片板块整体表现强劲。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">中大型无人机首次集群亮相春晚</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">春晚首次展示中大型无人机集群表演，低空经济热度升温，多地政策支持无人机产业发展。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">印度举办25万人AI峰会</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">印度首次举办超大规模AI峰会，25万人参与，号称\"有史以来规模最大\"，显示新兴市场对AI热情。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">🇺🇸 美股市场 (TOP 20)</h2>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">美股两连阳 科技七巨头齐涨</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">美股连续两个交易日上涨，科技七巨头（苹果、微软、谷歌、亚马逊、Meta、英伟达、特斯拉）全线收涨，市场情绪回暖。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">苹果涨超3%</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">苹果公司股价上涨超3%，此前公司宣布加大AI投资力度，iPhone AI功能备受期待。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">纳指涨0.78%</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">纳斯达克综合指数上涨0.78%，科技股领涨带动指数上行。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">存储概念股普涨</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">存储芯片板块普遍上涨，受益于AI数据中心需求旺盛，存储行业景气度回升。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">标普500指数小幅收涨</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">标普500指数小幅收涨，但始终难以突破7000点关口，显示市场观望情绪浓厚。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">美股高开高走</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">美股三大指数高开高走，市场对经济软着陆预期增强，投资者风险偏好回升。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">芯片巨头闪迪遭减持</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">存储芯片巨头闪迪遭重要股东减持，股价承压下跌，引发市场对存储行业估值担忧。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">谷歌与印度政府合作AI项目</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">谷歌DeepMind与印度政府建立合作伙伴关系，共同推进AI在印度的发展应用。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">谷歌推出Pixel10a智能手机</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">谷歌发布Pixel 10a手机，搭载自研AI芯片，进一步强化手机AI功能。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">美联储1月纪要：几乎所有与会者支持维持利率不变</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">美联储1月会议纪要显示，几乎所有官员支持维持当前利率不变，对降息保持耐心。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-19</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">高盛：预计6月首次降息</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">高盛经济学家预计美联储将在6月进行首次降息25个基点，随后在9月进行第二次降息。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-19</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">瑞银：预计一季度再降息1次</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">瑞银预计2026年一季度有望再降息1次，但下次降息推迟至夏季的风险上升。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-19</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">美联储对加息可能性进行讨论</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">美联储会议纪要首次明确讨论加息可能性，显示货币决策面临不确定性。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-19</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">首次讨论加息可能性</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">美联储在1月会议上首次明确讨论加息可能性，为未来政策调整预留空间。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-19</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">人民币全球支付占比3.13%</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">环球银行金融电信协会数据显示，人民币全球支付占比达3.13%，国际化进程持续推进。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">管涛：理解人民币汇率政策</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">管涛撰文分析人民币汇率政策，强调从兼顾内外均衡角度理解汇率走势。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">A股现金流龙头公司显现</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">分析显示4个行业企业自由现金流量为正，A股现金流龙头公司开始显现，投资价值凸显。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">程实：中国资本市场龙马精神</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">程实撰文看好中国资本市场，表示龙马精神，未来可期，建议关注科技创新领域机会。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">李迅雷：A股稳中向好 机会在科技</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">经济学家李迅雷认为A股稳中向好，投资机会主要集中在科技创新领域。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">🚀 科创板/热门板块</h2>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">半导体、光通信领涨科创板</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">科创板半导体和光通信板块领涨，受益于AI算力需求爆发，国产替代加速。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">禾信仪器涨近50%创历史新高</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">科创板禾信仪器股价涨近50%，创历史新高，受益于科学仪器国产化政策利好。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">春节档票房破20亿</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">2026年春节档电影票房突破20亿，上海出品《飞驰人生3》强势领跑，影视行业复苏明显。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">非遗成为过年氛围组</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">非物质文化遗产成为春节热门话题，各地文旅借势推广传统文化，吸引游客体验。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">海南出岛机票紧俏</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">海南出岛机票价格高涨，海口至上海机票高达11560元，假期出行需求旺盛。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">春节中段机票价格腰斩</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">大年初一机票价格比节前腰斩，节中飞行比高铁票还便宜，航空运力恢复常态。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">深港双城记：年轻人赚两边的钱</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">深港通关便利带动双城生活，2025年出入境港澳居民近1800万人次，较2019年增长近300%。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">岚图汽车获港股上市审批</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">岚图汽车港股上市最新进展：已获得全部前置监管审批，距离上市更近一步。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">芯天下港股IPO毛利率低于同行</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">芯天下冲刺港股IPO，主营产品毛利率低于行业平均水平，面临竞争压力。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <div class=\"news-title\">光芯片巨头进击AI 业绩激增1000%</div>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">光芯片巨头业绩预告激增1000%，受益于AI数据中心对光模块需求爆发。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <p>🤖 由 OpenClaw 自动生成 · 仅供参考，投资需谨慎</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>'''\n\nmsg = MIMEText(html, 'html', 'utf-8')\nmsg['From'] = 'nohotnnn@gmail.com'\nmsg['To'] = 'nohotnnn@gmail.com'\nmsg['Subject'] = Header('A股开盘前资讯 - 2026年2月19日', 'utf-8')\n\nsmtp = smtplib.SMTP('smtp.gmail.com', 587)\nsmtp.starttls()\nsmtp.login('nohotnnn@gmail.com', 'afwqopixqunpfgrf')\nsmtp.send_message(msg)\nsmtp.quit()\n\nprint(\"Sent!\")\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":26984,"output":5720,"cacheRead":13401,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46105,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse