{"type":"message","id":"d34a500e","parentId":"d318c513","timestamp":"2026-02-19T06:07:44.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Boss is asking where these records are stored. Let me explain:\n\n1. The cron job configuration is stored in the OpenClaw gateway's database - that's why we can query it with `cron list`\n2. The HTML template is at /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-v4.html\n\nLet me explain this clearly.","thinkingSignature":"74cd0b0b98d234c3030b4b4908095577ba68e08a61fb6a84db8f0b9a1206bc3e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n记录在两个地方：\n\n**1. 定时任务配置** - 存在 OpenClaw Gateway 数据库里\n- 用 `cron list` 查询的就是这里\n- 每次我修改都是调用 `cron update` 写入这里\n- 这个不会丢失，重启 gateway 也在\n\n**2. HTML 模板文件** - 本地磁盘\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-v4.html`\n- 这是样式参考模板\n\n---\n\n如果你想备份/导出配置，可以手动记录下来。或者我可以帮你写到 workspace 文件里，方便你查看和修改。要我创建一个配置说明文件吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":195,"cacheRead":7823,"cacheWrite":45644,"totalTokens":53690,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771481256631}}
