{"type":"message","id":"49e9a3ef","parentId":"c0628ced","timestamp":"2026-02-19T08:46:08.684Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The APK was built successfully. Let me summarize what was created for the user.","thinkingSignature":"36910aa28df04b013a02e85f17df8588d23d14aa3dc3290fbe1dbd630a58b07e"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **构建成功！**\n\nAPK 已生成：`/root/code/kid_app/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk` (7.7MB)\n\n**项目结构：**\n```\n/root/code/kid_app/\n├── app/\n│   └── src/main/\n│       ├── java/com/kidscore/app/\n│       │   ├── MainActivity.kt\n│       │   ├── data/\n│       │   │   ├── model/ParentingBehavior.kt  (数据模型)\n│       │   │   └── repository/ParentingKnowledgeBase.kt  (知识库 25条行为)\n│       │   ├── viewmodel/ScoreViewModel.kt\n│       │   └── ui/\n│       │       ├── theme/\n│       │       └── screens/ScoreScreen.kt\n│       └── res/\n├── build.gradle.kts\n└── gradle.properties\n```\n\n**功能：**\n- 输入育儿行为 → 显示评分(0-100) → 错误分析 + 改正建议\n- 内置 25 种常见行为知识库\n- Material Design 3 绿色主题\n\n可以安装到安卓手机测试了 📱"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":62299,"output":254,"cacheRead":13440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771490763214}}
