{"type":"message","id":"511efc3d","parentId":"fc648b8b","timestamp":"2026-02-19T08:47:38.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about an error that occurred during the development process. Looking at the message, it's from earlier when I tried to use Claude Code (claude CLI) to develop the app. The error was \"Not logged in · Please run /login\".\n\nThis happened because Claude Code requires authentication/logging in to use its AI features. Since we couldn't log in, I switched to manually writing the code using the read/write tools instead of using Claude Code.\n\nLet me explain this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"08b5484901254fac738b4041a06169e12ea7e02326c9f9c24ffdc203dd06b436"},{"type":"text","text":"这是之前尝试用 **Claude Code** 开发时遇到的错误：\n\n```\nNot logged in · Please run /login\n```\n\n**原因：** Claude Code（`claude` 命令行工具）需要登录账号才能使用 AI 功能。在这个服务器环境里没有登录权限。\n\n**解决方案：** 放弃 Claude Code，改为直接用我的工具（`write`/`read`/`exec`）手动编写所有代码。\n\n---\n\n不过你的本地环境如果已登录 Claude Code，可以直接用它来开发，速度会快很多：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/code/kid_app\nclaude -p \"帮我完善这个育儿评分App，增加xxx功能\"\n```\n\n要不要试试？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":235,"cacheRead":7822,"cacheWrite":68270,"totalTokens":76355,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771490825987}}
