{"type":"message","id":"22393592","parentId":"8d93c6c0","timestamp":"2026-02-19T09:02:24.194Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the SIGKILL failures were caused by Claude Code. Yes, that was the case - the Claude Code processes were being killed, likely due to:\n1. Timeout/resource constraints\n2. Network issues connecting to the custom base URL\n3. The environment killing long-running AI processes\n\nI confirmed this earlier when I tried to run Claude Code and it kept getting killed. I then provided a manual code review instead.","thinkingSignature":"223ae1b40414df28468feeb5d5bd8ce1a95eda8e92195fffdd129cb93b3d6a55"},{"type":"text","text":"是的，是 Claude Code 导致的。\n\n**原因推测：**\n1. 连接到自定义 Base URL (`38.12.4.246`) 的 AI 服务可能不稳定\n2. 进程运行时间稍长就被系统 Kill 掉了\n3. 这个环境可能对外部 AI 调用有资源限制\n\n**所以我后来改成手动 Review**，直接读取代码文件分析问题，没有调用 AI。\n\n---\n\n你的本地环境如果 Claude Code 能正常工作，可以这样运行：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/code/kid_app\nclaude -p \"对这个项目做Code Review\"\n```\n\n要不要我把项目同步到你本地，你用 Claude Code 再跑一次？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":220,"cacheRead":7822,"cacheWrite":71231,"totalTokens":79301,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771491727207}}
