{"type":"message","id":"9a2bef29","parentId":"003293ea","timestamp":"2026-02-19T14:08:50.154Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking where they can add some interesting Telegram groups. This is a question about finding Telegram groups, likely for Chinese/tech/investment related content that would be useful for the A-stock news task.\n\nLet me think about ways to find Telegram groups:\n1. Search on Google for Telegram group links\n2. Use Telegram group directories\n3. Ask in existing communities\n\nSince I can't access Telegram directly, I can suggest some ways to find interesting groups.","thinkingSignature":"0d349233d325b518e6651a3dafdba61dca17d5267470a688d5461881bb932405"},{"type":"text","text":"找 Telegram 群组的方法：\n\n**1. Google 搜索**\n```\nsite:t.me 关键词群\n例如: site:t.me A股 投资\nsite:t.me 人工智能 科技\nsite:t.me 编程 开发\n```\n\n**2. 导航目录**\n- https://telegramcn.me/ - 中文 Telegram 导航\n- https://t.me/ - 官方群组目录\n\n**3. 聚合平台**\n- https://www.sobatgaming.com/telegram-groups/ (英文为主)\n- 百度搜索 \"Telegram 群组 推荐\"\n\n**4. 常见优质中文群类型**\n- 币圈/量化交易群\n- 程序员技术群\n- 港股/美股交流群\n- AI/大模型讨论群\n\n---\n\n你想加什么类型的群？我可以帮你搜一下具体的群链接。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":274,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":79300,"totalTokens":79602,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771510082176}}
